body: SUDDENLY MY SICK, ELDERLY CHIHUAHUA CAN EAT AGAIN AND KEEP HIS FOOD DOWN!!! YAY!!! MY LITTLE DOG IS EATING AGAIN AND KEEPING HIS FOOD DOWN!!! I am so thrilled!!! Because of a few negative reviews, I had avoided Cesar's Classics & other Cesar's products.  BIG MISTAKE.. at least on my part.  Our little 16 year old Chihuahua has developed a heart murmur and kidney disease.  Per our veterinarian's advise, our "boy" was put on a special, prescription diet.  Unfortunately, he couldn't keep the prescription food down. I started him off slowly, mixing it bit by bit with his regular kibble.. which I regularly softened with bottled water.  It was okay the first day... but after that, he began throwing it up, having diarrhea, and then finally, just sniffing his food, and walking away.. It was so sad to watch his condition worsened. Our poor little old Chihuahua was becoming just skin and bones. I expected to lose him any moment. I was at my wits end, so in spite of the few, isolated, negative reviews I had read, I gave her the okay.  Suddenly.. just smelling the peeled open food,  my sick, skin & bones little guy "came alive" wiggling all over & wagging his tail! He reached for the tray before it was set down!!! It's a pet's mealtime miracle, and thankfully, is a true blessing for this little guy!!! Yes, this investment is a real hit on my grocery budget. Is it worth it? You Bet!!!
